            "id": 6011560,
            "title": "〈熱門股〉德儀傳調漲價格 矽力*-KY股價周漲10%站回月線",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>德儀 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TXN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TXN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TXN-US</a>) 本周傳出調漲部分產品價格，且平均漲幅達 1 成，業界看好，隨著德儀調漲價格，其他類比晶片業者也可望跟進，並有助整體產業環境優化，中國本土供應鏈也可望受惠，矽力 *-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6415:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6415\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6415-TW</a>) 受此消息激勵，股價站上月線大關，週漲 10.14%。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011560%2Fl%2Fc74652066f72ecab0872d7dbd7acb8c7.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">矽力資料照。(圖：擷取自官網)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>德儀此次傳出對部分產品線漲價，平均漲幅達 1 成以上，部分更上看 4 成至 7 成，預計 6 月 15 日正式生效，業界認為，隨著德儀殺價搶單策略轉變，整體產業的獲利率可望改善。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>矽力 *-KY 本周聞訊後，股價連日強漲，帶動股價從谷底翻揚，單周大漲 1 成，最高一度逼近 400 元，週五終場收在 385.5 元，三大法人僅外資站買方，外資狂買 779 張，投信小賣 45 張、自營商也小幅調節 13 張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-cnyeschart=\"cnyeschart\" src=\"https://so.cnyes.com/mobilechart/MobileChart.aspx?markettype=twstock&amp;charttype1=kchart&amp;stockcode=6415&amp;imgwidth=580&amp;imgheight=500&amp;bgcolor=2\"/>\n<figcaption> </figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
